Title: Annual Innovation Summit — Main Stage
Author: Example Production
Draft date: April 2026
Format: Secuens v0.9

===

CONFERENCE - MAIN STAGE - MORNING SESSION

Doors open. Audience files in.

[[AUDIO (cue 1) [file="pre_show_music.mp3", level=-18dB, loop=true]: Pre-show music — background]]
[[LIGHTS (cue 2) [preset=house_50, fade=0s]: House lights 50%]]

--- 30 MIN BEFORE SHOW ---

Audience mostly seated.

LIGHTS (cue 3) [fade=10s, preset=house_down]: House lights down — 20%

GRAPHICS (cue 4) [template=countdown, duration=600s, position=main_screen]: 10-minute countdown on screen

--- SHOWTIME ---

AUDIO (cue 5) [fade=3s]: Pre-show music fade out

LIGHTS (cue 6) [fade=3s, preset=blackout]: House to black

VIDEO (cue 7) [source=playback, file="summit_opener.mp4", audio=stereo]: Roll opener video — 2 min

Video ends. Screen goes dark.

LIGHTS (cue 8) [fade=3s, preset=stage_wash_warm]: Stage wash up — warm amber

AUDIO (cue 9) [source=playback, file="entrance_music.mp3", fade=1s]: Entrance music

GRAPHICS (cue 10) [template=lower_third, content="CEO — Jane Michaels", duration=8s]: Lower third — CEO name

Speaker walks to center stage. Applause.

CAMERA (cue 11) [preset=single_wide, transition=dissolve]: Camera 1 — speaker full

AUDIO (cue 12) [fade=2s]: Entrance music fade out

AUDIO (cue 13) [source=lav_1, gate=-22dB, compression=light]: Lavalier hot — speaker

SPEAKER (JANE MICHAELS)
Thank you all for being here today. This is our most important summit yet.

GRAPHICS (cue 14) [template=presentation, source=laptop_hdmi]: Display slide 1 — title

Speaker gestures to screen.

CAMERA (cue 15) [preset=single_tight, transition=cut]: Camera 2 — tighter on speaker

SPEAKER
Let's talk about what comes next.

GRAPHICS (cue 16) with slide advance: Display slide 2 — data

CAMERA (cue 17) [preset=wide_stage, speed=slow, transition=dissolve]: Camera 3 — wide pull back

The hall is full. Energy is high.

LIGHTS (cue 18) [fade=2s, preset=add_audience_wash]: Bring up audience wash — subtle

SPEAKER
I want to introduce someone who embodies everything we stand for.

AUDIO (cue 19) [source=playback, file="intro_sting.mp3", level=-6dB]: Short intro sting

GRAPHICS (cue 20) [template=full_screen, file="guest_intro.mp4", duration=30s]: Guest intro video

Video plays. Speaker steps aside.

GUEST walks on stage. Applause.

AUDIO (cue 21) [source=lav_2, gate=-22dB]: Guest lavalier hot

AUDIO (cue 22) [source=lav_1, gate=-40dB]: Speaker lav down — not off

CAMERA (cue 23) [preset=two_shot, transition=cut]: Camera 1 — two shot

LIGHTS (cue 24) [fade=2s, preset=two_person_special]: Add fill for two on stage

--- PANEL BEGINS ---

AUDIO (cue 25) [source=lav_1, gate=-22dB]: Speaker back up — panel begins

CAMERA (cue 26) [preset=panel_wide, transition=dissolve]: Wide shot — panel

End of morning session.

LIGHTS (cue 27) [fade=5s, preset=house_50]: House lights up — 50%

AUDIO (cue 28) [source=playback, file="break_music.mp3", level=-18dB, fade=3s]: Break music in

GRAPHICS (cue 29) [template=break_slide, content="Break — 15 minutes", position=main_screen]: Break slide

[[AUDIO (cue 30): Check all mics — battery levels before afternoon session]]
